{"tid":1777894,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（最有效黃色經濟圈）黃色博彩莊家","createTime":"2019-12-10T14:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T14:11:18.000Z","uid":145727,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"145ca378bba46306111f79ea8f11fe5f553f661a","tid":1777894,"uid":145727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"而家612 基金多數都係靠大家捐錢 <br />\n被捕人數咁多 未必夠錢支援<br />\n 大家亦都要付出現金支援 <br />\n但有冇諗過瞓喺到都大把錢收呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下只係鳩吹 一定犯法的 唔鼓勵咁做<br />\n但如果做到就犀利囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年博彩稅收<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">233億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係233億呀</span></span><br />\n大概喺投注額嘅10% <br />\n呢啲錢全部都係稅收嚟 <br />\n唔涉及社會福利用途 <br />\n如果有外圍黃色莊家 <br />\n可以有一定市場分額<br />\n假設喺一成 呢一部分嘅錢大部分捐比612 <br />\n小部分提高賠率 吸引人去玩 <br />\n一個月接近會有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2億</span></span>可以支援手足 <br />\n係而家嘅唔知幾多倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然好難實行 不過有啲國家係有合法嘅網上博彩牌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開頭資金未必需要太多</span><br />\n如果喺一啲只有機率嘅玩法 <br />\n例如 足球入球單雙 六合彩單雙<br />\n會比較容易控制 莊家輸嘅機率較低<br />\n個pool 亦都唔需要太多錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然賭仔係咪都要賭<br />\n賭黃莊家 又唔會洗多左錢 <br />\n賠率又靚啲<br />\n基金又有大額收入 <br />\n簡直係瞓喺度有錢收<br />\n<br />\n利申：香港只有狗會喺合法 <br />\n要買唔該出咗公海先好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5373633558d456656277f1d8b6db4ea424c493b","tid":1777894,"uid":145727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:02:40.000Z","msg":"10連<br />\n1/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5386c1ac73855c9af1d17428ad2df99c203964","tid":1777894,"uid":145727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:02:55.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"b7707243a3e148d97a1b812016055b1d14e96c8b","tid":1777894,"uid":145727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:04:19.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"4295c64bd8c5bc168c3cef32860f18c7f459e79b","tid":1777894,"uid":145727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"9e13f7d39469e43c4b6c46bd6058fa389af5e4bc","tid":1777894,"uid":145727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"0f590badfbe57dcbf153571abcc9faa3733cd07e","tid":1777894,"uid":145727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:08:36.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"be6a1ff2f04b291002423d5c7575643f6178c0ea","tid":1777894,"uid":335834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:10:00.000Z","msg":"攞正牌充公你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4b9bafb1dbec8ea2d6ae083c816af6bccaf351","tid":1777894,"uid":198035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"比人拉左十次都未籌到錢"},{"pid":"b31f47bc51d6d496e33facf68587978aa05c4af4","tid":1777894,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:11:01.000Z","msg":"即係搞下圍，做咩咁睇唔開<br />\n<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"872e1cf1e688f1b4e2fba1512ac39e68ea3e3a8c","tid":1777894,"uid":163704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b31f47bc51d6d496e33facf68587978aa05c4af4","tid":1777894,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi